about.description: Manage streaming data, optionally with Dask and Pandas
about.summary: Manage streaming data, optionally with Dask, Pandas and more

name: rapidz
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rapidz" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/xpdAcq/rapidz/releases/download/{{ version }}/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ff4c03dc965b1721399effcc13b407c3fcd38c44405ef1a5edfd28699f0c77cc

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - tornado
    - toolz
    - zict
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - rapidz
    - rapidz.core


about:
  home: https://github.com/xpdAcq/rapidz/
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "Manage streaming data, optionally with Dask, Pandas and more"

  description: |
    Manage streaming data, optionally with Dask and Pandas
  doc_url: https://xpdacq.github.io/rapidz/
  dev_url: https://github.com/xpdAcq/rapidz/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - CJ-Wright
